IF EXISTS(Select * from sysobjects where name = 'TempReport_Summary_Detail' and type = 'U')
BEGIN
EXEC dbo.CreateBackup 'dbo','TempReport_Summary_Detail'
DROP TABLE dbo.TempReport_Summary_Detail
END

Select CASE WHEN ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) = 0 THEN 'Included'
ELSE 'Rejected' END AS InSample
,Sou.[SourceName] AS SourceName
,S.GRSListId
,Grs.[GRSBucket] AS GRSBucket
,Seg.[SegmentName] AS SegmentName
,Sub.[SubSegment] AS SubSegmentName
,ET.[EngagementType] AS [EngagementType]
,DET.[DetailedEngagementType] AS [DetailedEngagementType]
,Com.[ActiveCompetencies] AS CompetancyLevel
,S.[CompanyName] AS CompanyName
,S.[AccountNumber] as AccountId
,S.[ContactNumber] as ContactId
,S.[MPNID] AS MPNID
,CASE WHEN S.KeyContact = 1 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS KeyContact
,CASE WHEN S.ManagedContact = 1 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS ManagedContact
,S.[FirstName] AS FirstName
,S.[LastName] AS LastName
,S.[EmailAddress] AS EmailAddress
,CASE WHEN S.AllowEmail = 1 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS AllowEmail
,S.[JobRole] AS JobRole
,S.[JobTitle] AS JobTitle
,MA.[MarketAudience] AS MarketAudience
,Pl.[Language] AS PreferredLanguageId
,S.[City] AS City
,S.[State] AS State
,S.[StreetAddress] AS StreetAddress
,S.[PostalCode] AS PostalCode
,C.[CountryName] AS CountryName
,S.AccountManager
,S.SubsidiaryID
,SR.SubsidiaryName
,SR.AreaName
,SR.RegionName
,SR.SubRegionName
,S.RejectionCount
,S.RejectionSubTypes
,ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) AS IsFixable
----------NonFixable
,(Case WHEN (ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%DNC Poland%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%DNC Germany%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%DNC France%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%DNC Canada%') AND (ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) !=0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 0) THEN 'X' ELSE '' END) AS DNCLocalSuppression
,'' AS DNCPriorWaveHardBounceBack
,(Case WHEN (ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%DNC MMDS Suppression%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Retail Survey Priority Suppression%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%OEM Survey Priority Suppression%')  AND (ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) !=0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 0) THEN 'X' ELSE '' END) AS OtherSurveySuppression
,(Case WHEN ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Geneva Undeliverable%' AND (ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) !=0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 0) THEN 'X' ELSE '' END) AS DNCMDMHardSuppress
,(Case WHEN (ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Local Suppression%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Hierarchy De-Duplication%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing IsMaps%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%NMP%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Partner Organization%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Geography Out of Scope%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing DetailedEngagementType%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing SubSegment%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing Segment%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%MSHK Competitor Suppression%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Russia Competitor Suppression%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Hard Bounce Back%'  
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%FAR Clause Suppression%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Prior Wave Survey DQ%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Competitor Suppression%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Company Wide Anti Survey Suppression%') AND (ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) !=0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 0) THEN 'X' ELSE '' END) AS OtherNonFixable
,(Case WHEN ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Global Company Suppression%' AND (ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) !=0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 0) THEN 'X' ELSE '' END) AS GlobalCompanySuppression
,(Case WHEN ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Duplicate records%' AND (ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) !=0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 0) THEN 'X' ELSE '' END) AS DeDupeinSameBucket
--------Fixable
,(Case WHEN (ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Survey Vendor Unsubscribe%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Non-Personal Emails%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Not In Managed List%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Geneva Undeliverable%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Dummy Emails%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Contact Preference%') AND (ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) !=0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 1) THEN 'X' ELSE '' END) AS OtherFixable
,(Case WHEN (ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing FirstName%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing LastName%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Invalid or Missing company name%')  AND (ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) !=0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 1) THEN 'X' ELSE '' END) AS MissingNameCompanyFirstLast
,(Case WHEN (ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing Email%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Invalid Email or Format%') AND (ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) !=0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 1) THEN 'X' ELSE '' END) AS InvalidMissingEmail
,(Case WHEN (ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing Country%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing SubsidiaryName%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing AccountManager%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing City (NMP Only)%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing ContactID%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing AccountID%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing Partner Number%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing Postal Code (US Only)%' 
OR ISNULL(S.RejectionSubTypes,'') like '%Missing Company Street Address%') AND (ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) !=0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 1) THEN 'X' ELSE '' END) AS InvalidMissingFields
INTO dbo.TempReport_Summary_Detail
FROM dbo.Scorecard S with(nolock)
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_Country] C with(nolock) ON S.[CountryId] = C.[CountryId]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_MarketAudience] MA with(nolock) ON S.[MarketAudienceID] = MA.[MarketAudienceID]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_Segment] Seg with(nolock) ON S.[SegmentId] = Seg.[SegmentId]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_SubSegment] Sub with(nolock) ON S.[SubSegmentId] = Sub.[SubSegmentId]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_ActiveCompetencies] Com with(nolock) ON S.[CompetencyID] = Com.[ID]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_Language] Pl with(nolock) ON S.[PreferredLanguageId] = Pl.[LanguageId]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_GRSList] Grs with(nolock) ON S.[GRSListID] = Grs.[GRSListID]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_Source] Sou with(nolock) ON S.[GRSDataSourceID] = Sou.[SourceId]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Reporting].[dbo].[SubsidiaryDetails] SR with(nolock) ON S.[SubsidiaryID] = SR.[SubsidiaryID]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_EngagementType] ET with(nolock) ON S.[EngagementTypeId] = ET.[EngagementTypeId]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_DetailedEngagementType] DET with(nolock) ON S.[DetailedEngagementTypeId] = DET.[DetailedEngagementTypeId]
WHERE 1=1


Update dbo.TempReport_Summary_Detail
Set GRSBucket = 'Customer - SMB MPAA'
Where GRSBucket = 'Customer -  SMB MPAA ITP'


Update dbo.TempReport_Summary_Detail
Set GRSBucket = 'Customer - SMB MPAA'
Where GRSBucket = 'Customer -  SMB MPAA BDM'

Update dbo.TempReport_Summary_Detail
Set MarketAudience = ''
Where MarketAudience = '0'

Update S
Set SubSegmentName = null
FROM [Vnxt_Reporting].[dbo].[TempReport_Summary_Detail] S with(nolock)
WHERE SubSegmentName = '0'


Update S
Set SegmentName = null
FROM [Vnxt_Reporting].[dbo].[TempReport_Summary_Detail] S with(nolock)
WHERE SegmentName = '0'

Update S
Set [DetailedEngagementType] = null
FROM [Vnxt_Reporting].[dbo].[TempReport_Summary_Detail] S with(nolock)
WHERE [DetailedEngagementType] = '0'

Update S
Set [EngagementType] = null
FROM [Vnxt_Reporting].[dbo].[TempReport_Summary_Detail] S with(nolock)
WHERE [EngagementType] = '0'

IF EXISTS(Select * from sysobjects where name = 'TempReport_Scorecard_Detail' and type = 'U')
BEGIN
EXEC dbo.CreateBackup 'dbo','TempReport_Scorecard_Detail'
DROP TABLE dbo.TempReport_Scorecard_Detail
END

Select 
Cla.Classification
,Grs.GRSBucket
,Sub.AreaName
,Sub.SubRegionName
,Count(1) AS TotalCount
,Count(CASE WHEN ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) = 0 THEN 1 END) AS SampleCount
,Count(CASE WHEN ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) != 0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 1 THEN 1 END) AS FixableRejectionCount
,Count(CASE WHEN ISNULL(S.RejectionCount,0) != 0 AND ISNULL(S.IsFixable,0) = 0 THEN 1 END) AS NonFixableRejectionCount
INTO dbo.TempReport_Scorecard_Detail
FROM [vnxt_Reporting].dbo.Scorecard S with(Nolock)
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Catalogues].[dbo].[Lkp_GRSList] Grs with(nolock)
ON S.[GRSListID] = Grs.[GRSListID]
LEFT JOIN [vnxt_Reporting].[dbo].[wk_Cat_Core_GRSLists] Cla with(nolock)
ON S.[GRSListID] = Cla.[GRSListID]
INNER JOIN [vnxt_Reporting].dbo.SubsidiaryDetails Sub with(nolock)
ON S.SubsidiaryId = Sub.SubsidiaryId
WHERE 1=1
Group By Cla.Classification
,Grs.GRSBucket
,Sub.AreaName
,Sub.SubRegionName


Update dbo.[TempReport_Scorecard_Detail]
Set GRSBucket = 'Customer - SMB MPAA'
Where GRSBucket = 'Customer -  SMB MPAA ITP'

Update dbo.[TempReport_Scorecard_Detail]
Set GRSBucket = 'Customer - SMB MPAA'
Where GRSBucket = 'Customer -  SMB MPAA BDM'
